-- Spanish Construction Group OHL Seeks to List Shares of Mexican Division
-- B y   T h o m a s   B l a c k
-- 2010-10-13T17:31:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/spanish-construction-group-ohl-seeks-to-list-shares-of-mexican-division.html
Obrascon Huarte Lain SA, the Spanish
construction company known as OHL, requested authorization from
the Mexican stock exchange to list shares of its Mexico unit,
OHL Concesiones Mexico SA.  The request includes a “mixed” public offer of the
Mexican unit’s shares, the stock exchange said in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Black in Monterrey at 
 tblack@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
